{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Students were asked to solve programming tasks with the assistance of ChatGPT-3.5 (freely available in Dec. 2023), and to participate in an online survey to report their experiences.The quantitative and qualitative analysis of the survey responses (n=298) provides novel insights into students' use of ChatGPT in a curricular course setting.",
    "The contribution of this paper is a summary of students' use patterns, and reflections on applying ChatGPT while solving programming exercises.",
    "The presented research thereby supports educator's understanding of students' applying GenAI tools.",
    "This is crucial to help inform and develop adequate forms of instruction and pedagogical approaches supporting the critical and reflective use of GenAI tools within computing education.",
    "GenAI and related tools have taken the world by storm [3]."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "GenAI and related tools have taken the world by storm [3]."
  ]
}